===Noun===
'''глаз''' (glaz) ''m'', глаза (glazá) ''pl''
:''Note on irregular forms — '''''{{Unicode|глаза́}}''''' is actually an old nominative [[dual]] form. The genitive plural in '''''глаз''''' is also an archaic form and was usual in [[Old Church Slavonic]] ''(глазъ)''. In the [[locative case]], the '''''[[ъ]]'''''-ending of O.C.S. has become '''[[у]]''' in the modern language: '''''{{Unicode|в глазу́}}'''''.''

